item.title: Video RTC · Over Printing
item.description: Create Multi-tenant Video Services over WebRTC for your Contact Center. Overview Over Printing feature allows to print a logo inside the remote frame. Instead of specific customisation you can use it to distribute video calls to several services with their own service logo. It’s very useful for a Call Center with many services operated with different profiles. Over Printing functionality is easy to configure inside our multi-flavor settings without specific coding.
